---
import BaseHead from '../../components/BaseHead.astro';
import Header from '../../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../../components/Footer.astro';
import { SITE_TITLE } from '../../consts';
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="zh-Hant">
	<head>
		<BaseHead title={`寫作教練 - ${SITE_TITLE}`} description="Vista 寫作陪伴計畫：協助您建立個人品牌，從部落格到出書。" />
		<style>
            /* Sub-page Styles */
            .lp-hero {
                background: var(--color-primary);
                color: white;
                padding: 6rem 1rem;
                text-align: center;
            }
            .lp-hero h1 { color: white; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; font-size: 3rem; }
            .lp-hero p { color: var(--gray-light); font-size: 1.4rem; max-width: 800px; margin: 0 auto 2rem; }
            
            .cta-btn {
                display: inline-block;
                padding: 1rem 3rem;
                background: var(--color-red);
                color: white;
                font-weight: bold;
                border-radius: 9999px;
                text-decoration: none;
                transition: transform 0.2s;
            }
            .cta-btn:hover { transform: scale(1.05); }

            .section { padding: 5rem 1rem; max-width: 900px; margin: 0 auto; }
            .section h2 { text-align: center; margin-bottom: 3rem; font-size: 2.25rem; }
            
            .pain-points {
                display: grid;
                grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
                gap: 2rem;
            }
            .pain-point {
                background: #fef2f2; /* Red-50 */
                padding: 2rem;
                border-radius: 12px;
                border-left: 4px solid var(--color-red);
            }
            .pain-point h3 { color: var(--color-red); margin-top: 0; }
            
            .solution-list li {
                font-size: 1.2rem;
                margin-bottom: 1rem;
                padding-left: 2rem;
                position: relative;
            }
            .solution-list li::before {
                content: '✨';
                position: absolute;
                left: 0;
            }

            .pricing-card {
                background: white;
                border: 2px solid var(--gray-light);
                border-radius: 16px;
                padding: 3rem;
                text-align: center;
                box-shadow: 0 10px 25px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
                max-width: 500px;
                margin: 3rem auto;
            }
            .price { font-size: 3rem; font-weight: 800; color: var(--color-primary); margin: 1rem 0; }
            .price span { font-size: 1rem; color: var(--gray); font-weight: 400; }
		</style>
	</head>
	<body>
		<Header />
		<main>
            <section class="lp-hero">
                <h1>讓寫作成為你最強的個人品牌槓桿</h1>
                <p>別讓你的專業知識被埋沒。透過有系統的寫作訓練，建立話語權，開啟職涯新機會。</p>
                <a href="#pricing" class="cta-btn">申請諮詢</a>
            </section>

            <section class="section">
                <h2>你是否也遇到這些問題？</h2>
                <div class="pain-points">
                    <div class="pain-point">
                        <h3>想寫但寫不出來</h3>
                        <p>坐在電腦前發呆，明明有很多想法，卻不知道如何下筆組織成文章。</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="pain-point">
                        <h3>寫了沒人看</h3>
                        <p>用心經營部落格，但流量始終沒有起色，不知道讀者想看什麼。</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="pain-point">
                        <h3>難以持之以恆</h3>
                        <p>總是三天捕魚兩天曬網，缺乏穩定產出的系統與紀律。</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </section>

            <section class="section" style="background-color: var(--color-warm-bg); border-radius: 20px;">
                <h2>Vista 寫作陪伴計畫</h2>
                <p style="font-size: 1.2rem; margin-bottom: 2rem;">
                    這不是一堂單向輸出的錄影課程，而是一個為期 3 個月的<b>實戰教練計畫</b>。我將手把手帶你走過從選題、架構到經營的每一步。
                </p>
                <ul class="solution-list">
                    <li><b>精準選題策略</b>：找出市場需求與你專業的交集點。</li>
                    <li><b>文章批改與回饋</b>：每週一對一作業批改，直接點出盲點。</li>
                    <li><b>建立寫作系統</b>：打造屬於你的靈感庫與產出流程，不再依賴靈感。</li>
                    <li><b>個人品牌定位</b>：協助你梳理職涯優勢，打造具辨識度的專家形象。</li>
                </ul>
            </section>

            <section class="section" id="pricing">
                <h2>投資你的未來</h2>
                <div class="pricing-card">
                    <h3>一對一教練陪跑</h3>
                    <div class="price">NT$ ??? <span>/ 3個月</span></div>
                    <p>每週 1 小時諮詢 + 無限次 Email 提問</p>
                    <ul style="text-align: left; margin: 2rem 0;">
                        <li>深度盤點個人優勢</li>
                        <li>客製化寫作課表</li>
                        <li>出版提案輔導 (加贈)</li>
                    </ul>
                    <a href="https://cal.com/iamvista" class="cta-btn" style="width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box;">預約面談評估</a>
                    <p style="font-size: 0.9rem; color: var(--gray); margin-top: 1rem;">* 為確保品質，每月僅收 3 名學員</p>
                </div>
            </section>
		</main>
		<Footer />
	</body>
</html>
